sheep-washing
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:the bathing of sheep prior to shearing, to clean the wool or to rid sheep of scab.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
